sql:
SELECT jersey_number, SUM(games_started) AS total_games_started
FROM players
WHERE player_name = 'Bourque, Logen';

SELECT p.player_name, p.games_played
FROM players p
WHERE p.hometown = 'Lubbock, TX';

external_knowledge:
- Cumulative points refer to the running total of points for each team in a division; 
- Total points are calculated by summing up the points scored by each team; 
- The teams are ordered in descending order based on their total points, so the teams with the highest points are listed first.
